            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "So should I put a compat check in to the session cookie samesite support so that Werkzeug 0.14 isn't required (and what version should I require instead)? Or should I not worry about compat, and bump the version to whatever is needed, when it's needed?\r\n\r\nWhat version should we bump Jinja to? 2.4 is *8 years old*, no one should be using that with Flask 1.0, but any other choice seems equally arbitrary."
